about.summary: A port of Ruby on Rails inflector to Python

name: inflection
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "inflection" %}
{% set version = "0.3.1" %}
{% set bundle = "tar.gz" %}
{% set hash_type = "sha256" %}
{% set hash_val = "18ea7fb7a7d152853386523def08736aa8c32636b047ade55f7578c4edeb16ca" %}

package:
  name: {{ name }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.{{ bundle }}
  {{ hash_type }}: {{ hash_val }}

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed --no-cache-dir -vvv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip

  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - inflection

about:
  home: https://github.com/jpvanhal/inflection
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'A port of Ruby on Rails inflector to Python'
  dev_url: https://github.com/jpvanhal/inflection
  doc_url: https://inflection.readthedocs.io/en/latest/

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - pmlandwehr
